diff --git a/changes/2492.misc.rst b/changes/2492.misc.md\nsimilarity index 100%\nrename from changes/2492.misc.rst\nrename to changes/2492.misc.md\ndiff --git a/changes/2493.misc.md b/changes/2493.misc.md\nnew file mode 100644\nindex 000000000..214156e14\n--- /dev/null\n+++ b/changes/2493.misc.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,1 @@\n+The `pre-commit` hook for `ruff-pre-commit` was updated to its latest version.\ndiff --git a/changes/2493.misc.rst b/changes/2493.misc.rst\ndeleted file mode 100644\nindex 0ac70ca93..000000000\n--- a/changes/2493.misc.rst\n+++ /dev/null\n@@ -1,1 +0,0 @@\n-The ``pre-commit`` hook for ``ruff-pre-commit`` was updated to its latest version.\ndiff --git a/changes/2495.bugfix.rst b/changes/2495.bugfix.md\nsimilarity index 100%\nrename from changes/2495.bugfix.rst\nrename to changes/2495.bugfix.md\ndiff --git a/changes/2497.feature.md b/changes/2497.feature.md\nnew file mode 100644\nindex 000000000..3655b16e8\n--- /dev/null\n+++ b/changes/2497.feature.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,1 @@\n+`briefcase dev` no longer overwrites explicitly set environment variables.\ndiff --git a/changes/2497.feature.rst b/changes/2497.feature.rst\ndeleted file mode 100644\nindex 580b9d8ae..000000000\n--- a/changes/2497.feature.rst\n+++ /dev/null\n@@ -1,1 +0,0 @@\n-``briefcase dev`` no longer overwrites explicitly set environment variables.\ndiff --git a/changes/2499.misc.rst b/changes/2499.misc.md\nsimilarity index 100%\nrename from changes/2499.misc.rst\nrename to changes/2499.misc.md\ndiff --git a/changes/2500.misc.md b/changes/2500.misc.md\nnew file mode 100644\nindex 000000000..214156e14\n--- /dev/null\n+++ b/changes/2500.misc.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,1 @@\n+The `pre-commit` hook for `ruff-pre-commit` was updated to its latest version.\ndiff --git a/changes/2500.misc.rst b/changes/2500.misc.rst\ndeleted file mode 100644\nindex 0ac70ca93..000000000\n--- a/changes/2500.misc.rst\n+++ /dev/null\n@@ -1,1 +0,0 @@\n-The ``pre-commit`` hook for ``ruff-pre-commit`` was updated to its latest version.\ndiff --git